00:05:33.020 --> 00:05:34.550
going to keep going.

00:05:34.550 --> 00:05:34.890
Right?

00:05:34.890 --> 00:05:36.480
They're going to keep going
until they can maybe bounce

00:05:36.480 --> 00:05:37.280
off of that wall.

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:40.110
So right when I blow away this
